Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:07.29,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a child, I dreamed \Nof being a hero of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:11.12,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "dreamed"? \NDid you give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:13.85,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.53,0:00:16.84,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Being a hero is a limited-time thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:20.38,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And when you grow up, it's difficult \Nto call yourself one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.92,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish it hadn't taken me so long to realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.93,0:00:26.33,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:27.92,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you can't help it now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:29.87,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.87,0:00:31.47,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:33.00,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:36.43,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since you can't, I'll become one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:41.56,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're an adult now, so it's too \Nlate for you, but I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.24,0:00:44.90,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave your dream to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:48.63,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:53.76,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel better...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what was the urgent \Nerrand from Kuzuki-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:38.02,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(275,488)}#05    Dancing After School
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.94,0:02:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All she said was,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"I have to finish the errand Kuzuki-sensei \Nasked me to do tonight or else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, Sakura-chan and Saber-chan, \Ntry to get along."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't go into detail. She just left...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, she's the one who suggested \Nyou stay over, and she splits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:03:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's okay. It gave me a chance to \Nchat with Saber-san about things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sakura and I understand one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There will be a lot of people at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, didn't you say yesterday \Nthat school was safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou, that was yesterday. It doesn't \Nmean that it's still safe today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna talk like that, I won't \Never be able to go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you need to conserve \Nyour mana, so get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, if that is your decision, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if you run into an emergency \Nsituation, use a Command Seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:03:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Do I have something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:13.85,Name,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Self-Study
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:26.74,Name,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Student Council Room
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Issei, aren't you going to eat lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to sleep now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Did you stay up all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just haven't been sleeping well lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Issei, someone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care! Tell them the student council is closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.53,0:04:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kuzuki-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuudou, I need to speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then she hasn't gone home, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon the intrusion. I felt I should inform \Nyou, as school is likely to end early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Issei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're not exactly an outsider, so I \Nguess it's okay for you to hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Late last night, a family called the faculty office,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,reporting that their daughter hadn't come \Nhome from archery club practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Based on what they learned from \Nthe other club members,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,they determined that Shinji was the last \None to talk to the missing student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Shinji wasn't at practice yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, a first-year student \Nforgot something at the dojo,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and when he came back for it, he saw Shinji \Nand the missing student arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We tried to confirm this with Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But he's absent today, and no \None's been able to reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't keep me in suspense, Issei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the missing student?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.58,0:06:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuzuri Ayako,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the captain of the archery team.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you notice anything odd about \NShinji's behavior yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen him very often lately, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You wouldn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I shouldn't have asked you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know my brother better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing for you to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:13.63,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All after-school club meetings are canceled today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:15.66,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The library will also be closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:20.59,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Students with no urgent business are \Nasked to leave school grounds at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:21.80,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for Ayako-chan, \Nshe's home sick today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Mitsuzuri comes tomorrow, \Ndon't mention this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tohsaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy, coming to school \Nwithout your Servant?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What choice did I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber can't dematerialize, so I can't bring her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then stay home from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Master strolling around without his Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,may as well be holding a sign \Nthat reads, "Please kill me."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emiya-kun, do you have any idea \Nhow big an idiot you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Masters don't fight with other people around, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So school should be perfectly safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell me this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see any others here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Finally sinking in, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, this morning, I went \Nfrom exasperated to pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"After all I told him, why is he doing everything \Nhe can to get himself killed?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Magic Crest...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is the incarnation of the magic \Npassed down in my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Simply by passing mana through it, \NI can invoke any spell etched here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.16,0:09:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've sent Archer away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.91,0:09:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Gandr Shot here will suffice for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gandr? Isn't that just a simple Nordic curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... A perfectly simple curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Tohsaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy? We're at school!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we make a scene, someone might come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll worry about that when it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My policy is not to miss an opportunity \Nwhen it presents itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Emiya-kun, but I'll deal with you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if you keep bumbling around like \Ntoday, I don't think my nerves can take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to fight you—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you don't, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just prepare yourself, Shirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:56.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was Gandr?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:10:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from what I know!\NAre you trying to kill me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I made that clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You could really hurt someone with those things!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't like pain, stand still!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish you off quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If they hit a vital spot, you'll die instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't sound like a mercy killing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Then quit running around!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting worked up because \Nmy target won't stand still!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:54.56,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Das Schließen Vogelkäfig... Echo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She put up a Bounded Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:09.61,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fixierung, Eilesalve!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.78,0:11:11.27,Default - italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trace on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's out of mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally came out, Emiya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put down that silly weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a chance of winning, Emiya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't know until I try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is your final warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put down your weapon, and give \Nme your Command Seals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At worst, I'll strip the nerves from your arm, \Nbut better to lose those than your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I cannot give you the Command Seals!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's no different from telling me to betray Saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's your life, so it's your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's three seconds. \NEmiya-kun, what's your decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tohsaka, was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Emiya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she's just unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.19,0:13:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't just unconscious! \NCan't you see she's been drained dry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drained dry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of her mana... Her life force, if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She hardly has any blood left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't do something, she'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Die? Hey, Tohsaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to stabilize her with this gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tohsaka, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.15,0:13:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're bleeding... \NYou're bleeding badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-Doesn't that hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts... It hurts like you wouldn't believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tohsaka, take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She vanished?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised. You aren't going \Nto use a Command Seal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I don't have many left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.79,0:14:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike my Master, you possess courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I will take a different tack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall give you a merciful death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to the other Servants, \Nyou aren't very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't pack any punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is the end for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were at my mercy all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... What was that amusing \Nthing you were saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something about my being \Ninferior to other Servants?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That won't do at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start by plucking out those eyes \Nthat were so dearly mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll move on to your remaining limbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:16:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emiya-kun, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-We have to stop this bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emiya-kun, do you have anything \NI can wrap it with?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Oh, I have a handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura always prepares them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like minds, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's better than nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Together with my towel, we can make do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, that woman was a Servant?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She attacked out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tell who it was, but doesn't that mean \Nthere's another Master here besides us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They finally made their move, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I've patched you up for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tohsaka, what happened with that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's better. I think she's out of the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you staring at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just so you know, I'd never \Ndo something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.56,0:17:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'd never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about our fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want to keep at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tohsaka? I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to. Let's call it a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.70,0:17:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For one thing, I owe you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get your wound treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please bear it until we get to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put simply, there's another Master at school,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,doing what was done to that girl again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.27,0:17:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To win the Holy Grail War, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.94,0:18:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Their plan is to sacrifice the students \Nto strengthen their own Servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are they nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? But there's already a \NBounded Field around the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once it's activated, everyone inside \Nwill probably weaken and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emiya-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Coming from me, you might reject this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I think we should call a truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A truce? Between you and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to deal with this other Master first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So until then, want to call a truce \Nand help me track them down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Personally, I think it's a good deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll feel better about my \Nchances with your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really helping you. \NWe've simply agreed to a ceasefire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as you don't betray \Nme, I'll assist you, Emiya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're on my side for good, then. \NLet's do our best, Tohsaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be quite that long, but try \Nto make yourself useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.56,0:19:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't a legitimate heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your father died before he could \Npass his Magic Crest on to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not so sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was always against my becoming a mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that contradictory?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.11,0:19:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It always seemed like Dad only taught \Nme because I refused to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.39,0:19:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, he only taught me strengthening magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so that's all I can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on... Why would you tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tohsaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Emiya-kun, we might be \Npartners for the time being,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but mages should always keep their arts secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of hiding it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:20:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad always said that magic isn't something \Nyou should go out of your way to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He really said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think he was trying to say to \Nnot let myself be bound by rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He always said to quit if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous! Your father was no mage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If he trained you, I can't recognize you as a mage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know I can't call myself a mage, \Nbut my dad was the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.93,0:20:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I do have a problem with your lack of training.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do? My old man's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's the inherent limit of a single mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mages never know when they'll die, \Nso they leave behind a Magic Crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:21:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was just angry at your father for not \Ntaking the proper steps to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Magic is the culmination of lifetimes of work,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,handed down from parent to child, \Nfor generation after generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The instant a child is born into a mage family,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that child becomes heir and successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the reason we're born, \Nand it's what we die for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A mage family's duty is to take the \Nhuman child they gave birth to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and turn it into something else, \Nover long years of rigorous training.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why your father was no mage, Emiya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He put being a father ahead of being a mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.85,0:23:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this Ryuudou Temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.27,0:23:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be so stiff, Emiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.48,0:23:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All the people in this town belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.19,0:23:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although I am inexperienced, I am still a mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.19,0:23:39.99,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(512,1)}Next Time \NMirage
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.24,0:23:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to pass, then force your way through.
